{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6bce40876f","title":"罗迦陵的主要右派论点","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"584f1ad4ea","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"6bce40876f"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"38e8ccddf6","name":"罗迦陵"},{"id":"f3874b2bcd","name":"城市建设部"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"76d04b39bb","type":"title","text":"罗迦陵的主要右派论点","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"b55fb67b3a","type":"authors","text":"城市建设部罗迦陵","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"1403c0485b","type":"subtitle","text":"(罗迦陵：任职城市建设部城市建设出版社编辑、翻译)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"0b577a83a6","type":"paragraph","text":"1．同意钱煇焴的九点意见：如(1)拿起武器来闹革命才是“狂风暴雨”，开会提意见，谈什么也是“和风细雨”；(2)认为肃反事实不够不应斗争；斗后没有逮捕的都是斗错的；肃反斗错的人多；(3)认为人事档案可以公开等。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"ad8aecc35d","type":"paragraph","text":"2．认为城市建设出版社一团糟，应当关门。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"50b65cc7cf","type":"paragraph","text":"3．对领导不满，认为何文不熟悉业务，办公室主任刘兰池文化低，不适于领导出版社，并说：“何文不走我走”，“回上海扫厕所也比在出版社强”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"4b5a3248a9","type":"paragraph","text":"4．认为现在大学生的待遇还不如一个初中程度的普通工人，甚至比资本主义国家的还低；现在人民生活太低，要求在生活资料上多投些资。反对党的社会主义工业化方针。并说“人人为下代，谁为我们这一代呢?”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"b4397f6bac","type":"paragraph","text":"5．当报上出现反批评时，认为是教条主义，不能说服人。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"80aaea74da","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957年7月(城市建设出版社整理)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"},{"id":"a509cdcdd4","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《城市建设部整风办公室编印“整风通讯”第三期》，1957年；钱煇焴提供。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f"}],"page":{"id":"285e841f8d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6bce40876f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}